<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12506</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17681</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>蟾蜍太太住在一个又臭又脏的沼泽地里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17682</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24525</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她把拇指姑娘带到了附近小溪里的睡莲叶子上面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24526</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29897</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这就是你的新家。”蟾蜍太太说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29898</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34361</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不喜欢这里。”拇指姑娘说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34362</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43098</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那也没有办法。”蟾蜍太太说，“你哪里也不能去。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43099</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48499</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>说完，蟾蜍太太消失在了黑暗中。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48500</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51494</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘很害怕。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51495</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58759</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她周围都是水，没有路可以逃走。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58760</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72291</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我想妈妈。”她小声地说，然后哭着睡着了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72292</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77628</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天早上，蟾蜍太太起得很早。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77629</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80689</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她叫醒了自己的儿子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80690</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88011</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“克罗克！我们去见你的新娘吧。”她兴奋地说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88012</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91201</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你要好好表现。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91202</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98804</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>克罗克慢慢地眨了眨眼睛。“好的，妈妈。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98804</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103106</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘刚刚醒来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103106</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109262</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真是一个可怕的梦！”她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109263</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112875</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她睁开眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112876</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117697</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>两只蟾蜍正盯着她看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117698</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121698</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘也盯着他们看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121699</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126363</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>克罗克比他的妈妈还要大。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126364</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133493</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“原来我不是在作梦。”拇指姑娘伤心地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133494</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140696</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是克罗克，你未来的丈夫。” 蟾蜍太太对她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140697</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145949</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她很漂亮，妈妈。”克罗克说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145950</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149850</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然他的眼睛动了一下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149851</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153333</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一只小苍蝇飞了过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153334</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160498</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>克罗克快速伸出黏黏的舌头，吃掉了那只苍蝇。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160499</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164667</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真恶心！”拇指姑娘说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164668</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171215</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在你们互相了解了解对方。”蟾蜍太太说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171216</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175655</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我去准备你们的婚礼。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175656</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178721</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她跳着离开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178761</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184898</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“请带我回家。”拇指姑娘恳求道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184899</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187724</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>克罗克摇了摇头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187725</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195671</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“妈妈会生气的。你不能惹妈妈生气。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195672</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201825</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是我不想和你结婚。”拇指姑娘说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201826</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208290</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>克罗克大声得打了个嗝。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208291</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212548</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这让拇指姑娘更加讨厌他了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212549</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215914</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会做一个很好的丈夫的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215915</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225030</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我可以抓住所有的虫子。”他自夸道，“你看。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225031</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230895</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这个时候，一只美丽的蝴蝶飞过。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230896</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238829</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快看我！”克罗克跳进了水里，水花溅到了拇指姑娘身上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238830</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245033</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他从一个叶子上跳到另一个叶子上，追赶那只蝴蝶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245034</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249217</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘忍不住了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249218</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253897</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“克罗克！”她大声叫道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>253898</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>259368</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“放走那只蝴蝶，你这个以强欺弱的坏蛋！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>259369</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265288</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>克罗克停了下来，然后大哭起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>265289</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>274750</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要告诉妈妈！”他大叫着跳走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>274751</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>280764</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘看到那只蝴蝶安全地飞走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>280765</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>284772</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也要逃走！”她大声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>284773</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>290422</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“也许我们可以帮你。”一个声音说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>290423</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>294135</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谁在说话？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>294136</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>296885</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘看了看周围。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>296886</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>299479</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她什么都没看到。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>299480</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>304211</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我在下面。”那个声音说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>304212</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>309223</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘往水下看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>309224</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>312223</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她看到了一群鱼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>312224</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>316483</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>其中一只正在看着她。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>316484</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>323488</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“克罗克觉得吓唬别人很有意思。”那只鱼说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>323489</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>327981</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我看也是。”拇指姑娘说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>327982</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>340243</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别担心。”那条鱼说，“我们会帮你逃走的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>